red.noise.pd<-ts(t$spec,frequency = 2500,start = 1)
red.noise.pd.ma<-ma(red.noise.pd, order = 100)
plot.ts(cbind(red.noise.pd, red.noise.pd.ma), plot.type = 'single', col = c('black', 'red'),lwd=c(1,2))
